<li>Latest stable release: 2013Q2</li>
<li><a href="http://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/pkgsrc/packages/">Binary Packages</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/pkgsrc/stable/pkgsrc.tar.gz">stable tgz</a></li>
